                <p>Discover the power of JavaScript to create interactive web experiences.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature">
                <img src="img/test.png" alt="Coding Challenges">
                <h3>Coding Challenges</h3>
                <p>Test your skills and grow through challenges.</p>
